articles.title: Jordan Clarkson bats for Jalen Green to play for Gilas Pilipinas - Rappler
articles.description: 'The next thing we got to work on is get Jalen in those [Gilas Pilipinas] jerseys,' says Jordan Clarkson of his fellow Filipino-American Jalen Green
articles.content: "To come out here and play the game I love, just having the Filipino country on my back, I'm always grateful," Green said. Rappler.com
